{"type":"text","timestamp":1782534561198,"sessionID":"ses_0f8b84a87ffeugHsJw5ZQ49CGn","part":{"id":"prt_f0756b2bd001CWXyKrhqpqQ8ne","messageID":"msg_f0756a804001f0vedAVzMMuOvZ","sessionID":"ses_0f8b84a87ffeugHsJw5ZQ49CGn","type":"text","text":"Implemented this phase-01 batch for route/theme/localization surfaces and recorded the authority updates.\n\nChanged files:\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj`: added `routeLabel`, `routeLabelByPath`, `routeWithArgs`, and `primaryActionLabel` so route inventory and shell labels stay source-aligned and resource-backed.\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj`: removed hard-coded route/shell labels, reused router label helpers, and switched the primary shell button to the shared theme color.\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/common/foodike_theme.cj`: added a small shared theme-contract module for source palette, shape radii, and body typography baseline.\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie/phase01_resource_theme_contract_test.cj`: added focused phase-01 verification for route ids, route arg composition, resource-backed labels, and theme constants.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`: updated 6 batch rows to `implemented` with concrete source behavior, target behavior, endpoints, and harness-blocked verification evidence.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`: synced by authority patch tool.\n- `translation-inputs/platform-capability-check.json`: updated `localization-resources` notes/strategy/endpoints/tests for this batch’s resource-backed shell-label work.\n- `translation-inputs/platform-capability-check.md`: synced by authority patch tool.\n\nCommands run:\n- `cjpm test` in `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony\\entry\\src\\test\\cangjie`\n- `python ...\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix ...`\n- `python ...\\patch_authority.py --kind platform ...`\n\nBuild result:\n- FAIL for focused test reproduction.\n- `cjpm test` is blocked before test execution because root package `ohos_app_cangjie_entry` imports `kit.AbilityKit`, `kit.ArkUI`, and `ohos.resource` without matching dependency declarations in `entry/cjpm.toml`.\n\nPlan changes:\n- none\n\nDeferred issues:\n- Test harness blocker: `entry/cjpm.toml` package wiring does not currently satisfy imported `kit.AbilityKit`, `kit.ArkUI`, and `ohos.resource` for `cjpm test`. Recorded as harness-blocked evidence in the updated matrix rows.\n- I did not change broader phase-01 open rows outside this requested batch.\n\nNext recommended action:\n- Fix the `entry/cjpm.toml` dependency wiring for the existing imported HarmonyOS kits, then rerun the target test package so the new phase-01 contract test can become compile/pass evidence instead of harness-blocked evidence.","time":{"start":1782534550205,"end":1782534561197}}}
